cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.FL, cs.DS

This paper deals with controller synthesis for LTL objectives, which is a topic in formal methods and logic. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also involves automata theory, which suggests cs.PL (Programming Languages) as a possible category. Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation and performance of the proposed method, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper mentions the SyntComp competition, which is related to formal verification and could place the paper in cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory).
